git init : build a respo(.git directory)
git add :  track the file which  git add
git commit -m : commit the file with the message
----------------------------------------------------------------
Untracked			Unmodified			Modified		Staged
	|					|			    	|		   	   |
	|---------------------Add the file-------------------->|
	|					|---Edit the file-->|			   |
	|<-Remove the file--|					|			   |
	|					|<-------------Commit--------------|
-----------------------------------------------------------------





